result: Hello Bradley! I wish you all the best to your 18th Birthday. I hope you had an amazing day with your friends and also your family. It‘s a long time ago since we met the last time, i hope we will see us next year finally again. \n\nYour best friend Fabian.

Hello Bradley! I wish you all the best to your 18th Birthday. I'm glad to see you have the best future ahead of you. I‘m so happy to have somebody like you as a friend. I’m glad to see you soon again.‬
We're going to have a great time when i will visit you in the USA.

Best regard, your best friend Fabian

Hello Bradley! I wish you all the best to your 18th birthday! I hope you are having a great year and will be enjoying your new year in the city of New Orleans! I‘m so happy to see you soon again when i‘ll will visit you next year. I‘m proud to have you as my friend Bradley.\n\nBest regards, Fabian.

Me and my friends spend one week in Crostia a few weeks ago. We rented a big house near to the sea and it took us more than 8 hours to get there. We spend our days with doing sports, drinking alcohol, smoking pipe and having a lot of fun like a big family. I hope that we will do a trip like that the next year again.

Me and my friends spend one week in croatia. We rented a big house and we eat a lot of food every day.\nThe biggest problem in the vacarion were our neighbours. There were many things that were wrong with them, like complaining about the loud music or doing party outside the house. But in the end they just ignored us, so we could have a great time over there. But I guess we won‘t go there again next year.

Me and my friends spend one week in croatia a few weeks ago. We had a great time over there . We also did a little trip to a beach but didn’t except that it was a stone beach. We also drunk a lot of beer all the time and I‘m sure we had a lot of fun. Next year we plan to go back to croatia but i guess to another house.
